{"type": "article", "id": 44139, "title": "日全食要横跨全境，美国邮政做了套漂亮的纪念品｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-08-15T23:10:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 29219, "name": "Ingo Maurer"}, {"id": 30564, "name": "OTOTO"}, {"id": 43241, "name": "USPS"}, {"id": 6627, "name": "Glow"}, {"id": 43242, "name": "Journey Group"}, {"id": 43243, "name": "韩旭东"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 111, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170815190308XkCVwzQN3bFuL6TR.jpeg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Total Eclipse of the Sun by USPS &amp; Journey Group</h3><p>8 月 21 日，美国人将有机会目睹一场境内大部分范围可见的日全食，美国邮政（<a href=\"https://www.usps.com/welcome.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">USPS</a>）为此发行了一款名为 <a href=\"https://store.usps.com/store/browse/productDetailSingleSku.jsp?productId=S_475304\" rel=\"nofollow\">Total Eclipse of the Sun</a> 的热敏纪念邮票，并联手设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.journeygroup.com/about\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jorney Group</a> 打造了一份特殊的包装。这本边长为 12.7 厘米的折页小册子本身就是一张解析日全食的信息图，标注了过境时的若干个阶段。在塑料外壳背面有一个圆形镂空以及蓝色小点，如果错过某个阶段，只要移动外壳让小点重合就能进行“回看”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190326rVbGYLe34H7fjcNq.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708151903275p4m6SIM0GLFayHB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190326hNf7TnMIgCyYiS6c.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190326TiWZDQVtsISrpfR2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Glow</h3><p>从冰箱里拿完东西忘关柜门或者离家前没有关掉某些电器，都有可能日积月累造成电力浪费。为了帮助人们更好地节电，美国初创企业 <a href=\"http://meetglow.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Glow</a> 历时四年研发了这款同名的耗电感应器。它基于磁阻感应技术运行，只要事先将传感器安装到电表上就能通过感应灯了解室内的耗电情况，配套的手机应用还会就电量激增向用户发送提示。根据介绍，Glow 可以节省至少 10% 的电费。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1178650747/glow-the-smart-energy-tracker-for-your-home\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 149 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190356TQK8BVuyoHa9pwmE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190356gat6QAojHOM5rf9W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190357Oy3rbBunUX8WZKlP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.809917\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190356wQmGIWgb6po2Y7dE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Spaghetti Monster by Lior Rokah Kor</h3><p>你听说过飞天面条神教吗？现在你可以委托意面怪兽在下厨时助你一臂之力了。曾为以色列设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 设计过<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/34506.html\">马克笔油刷</a>的 Lior Rokah Kor 带来了这个造型相当讨巧的意面滤锅，铺满面条后看起来还挺可爱的。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.ototodesign.com/collections/all-products/products/spaghetti-monster-colander\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 18 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190547hdUC6YDjX2J3lyin.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675676\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190547tX8B0A9kwQgV7dRp.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190547dTB4eYD6sobVF8Ej.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Blow Me Up by Theo Möller &amp; Ingo Maurer</h3><p>长长的灯管运输起来不方便，把它缩小放进罐头里如何？最近，德国设计师 Theo Möller 与灯具设计公司 <a href=\"https://www.ingo-maurer.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ingo Maurer</a> 联手打造了这款名为 Blow Me Up 的充气式灯具。使用时只要将灯管摊开、打气，再将电线接入即可。LED 灯条的一端配备了感应开关，将手贴近后便会自动点亮。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190430t9bmjO0YG4qLEUi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749219\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190429ZfE3Y7oIV9hOiyrc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190430njzhXTAPNbcmOkC5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190429RJXaN6xskreYpPgQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334568\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190429wrEM6qixSeCOBzRU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334568\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kamaboko by hirononf20</h3><p>被意译为鱼板的蒲鉾（Kamaboko）是日本一种常见的装饰用食物，最近 Twitter 上的日本网民 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hirononf20\" rel=\"nofollow\">hirononf20</a> 就以它尚未切成片的形态为灵感，设计了一套鱼板家具。家具由四片超大鱼板和可以滑动的木制基座组成，鱼板不仅可以单独当作沙发，还能侧放后将基座架起变身为一张桌子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190453zc7v92homLXknEgU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190453CU8K7AXtvapmPGJe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017081519045382S6MqZ1kyKTjgz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Snorkeling by 韩旭东</h3><p>在网络质量较差的情况下浏览图片时，有一部分会因为载入问题以像素格的形式呈现。台湾艺术家<a href=\"http://blog.xuite.net/hsutunghan6/wood\" rel=\"nofollow\">韩旭东</a>热衷于通过木块的借位，将这种科技带来的“瑕疵”与传统的木雕工艺结合在一起。这尊<a href=\"http://blog.xuite.net/hsutunghan6/wood/520838594\" rel=\"nofollow\">浮潜</a>者的木雕是他的最新作品，其中的一部分木块就像是呼吸时产生的气泡，营造出微妙的动态感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190504aB6R3EDIYLcJO2vu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815190504d21hijVaCAPJzIvF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.524000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017081519050496etEpvcU7bGw4xr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}